{"tid":810661,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[P牌仔] 完全唔識搵位泊街","createTime":"2018-09-08T07:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T15:25:55.000Z","uid":47824,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"31f42b4175d33275928f6753dfa5cde7642412c4","tid":810661,"uid":47824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:02:25.000Z","msg":"講返小小背景<br />\n小弟住東涌，渣左3、4個月車，問題就係我成日由東涌渣出去市區，去到市區完全唔識搵到位置比我泊低<br />\n<br />\n剩係識導航由A point 去 B point，但係到左B point 附近無乜位就荒失失，因為我唔知應該渣去邊，同完全唔識點行，唔知點搵位泊，除非去停車場，但係咁樣我就永遠學唔識搵街位泊<br />\n<br />\n依個問題應該點去改善？"},{"pid":"029c8ece62acc3a62b75302e6abae36dc8c8708e","tid":810661,"uid":77136,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"係大街double park就得啦 搵咩位吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eddf9e96a44e4dcd2bc3ce98ff76c9f712dccbf","tid":810661,"uid":54216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"永遠泊停車場囉"},{"pid":"513c6f98094d28b8625182c64c5c994c6b6e1fc9","tid":810661,"uid":150556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"有父幹，打電話問老豆泊邊就ok"},{"pid":"9eb1ada53a167ccf24f92e7968668706bd51bd98","tid":810661,"uid":6530,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:06:34.000Z","msg":"三百二任泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8952d65cd77890badae3194fb53f5c134ab2e10c","tid":810661,"uid":23499,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"渣得車就唔好慳停車場啦<br />\n如果要慳就唔好渣車<br />\n<br />\n最撚憎人係街亂鳩咁泊"},{"pid":"37a0cf80a81507b42859686289122e18a81b5507","tid":810661,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:10:22.000Z","msg":"其實你應該搵定目的地附近有冇咪錶..."},{"pid":"d6007ed929c5eaead682f6e7d8e06f408074a99d","tid":810661,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:10:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi